@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_fjpavs(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = ((wp.cos(v1 + 0.50) / wp.sin(tmp + 0.56)) * v1)
    tmp = v1
    v1 = wp.exp(v1)
    v2 = ((wp.abs(v2 + 0.58) / (v2 + 0.46 + tmp + 0.78)) / (wp.abs(v0 + 0.28) * (v2 + 0.51 + v2 + 0.44)))
    data[tid] = v0
